<br />

<br />
I have a question, which I can't seem to find on the search function.
<br />

<br />
I have *heard* of bards kiting those d*mn exploding spiders during the Manaetic Behemouth encounter while the rest of the raid force is busy killing the MB.
<br />

<br />
Of course, trying to find this information myself, and I can't.
<br />

<br />
So, is it possible?
<br />
What song line up would be best?
<br />
And what strategies is best employed?
<br />

<br />
Thanks for your time.</span></td>
