				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: PoI MB encounter: kiting the spiders<a name="20329"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Feb 10 04 3:35 PM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>Photo is correct...it takes a lot of people.  Which generally isn't a problem as folks want to come out for the flag.  Kiting in this event is an act of desperation imo.
<br />

<br />
When we do this we have a mezzer in a high dps group at each of the four rooms that lead to MBs lair.  The mezzer is there to keep the spiders occupied just long enough for the DPS team to take it out.  We begin early mezzing and ganking to get the flow of the spiders (these speed up as MB is engaged). In addition we have a floating DPS group that is in the hallway leading to MBs lair.  In the event that we get off our groove I have a macroed line /rs SE room needs HELP!.
<br />

<br />
</span></td>
