				<td colspan="2"><span>They are level 55 I think.  Not sure whether or not they are charmable.  They spawn every 10 to 15 seconds so not sure what you mean about the kill rate being enough to keep them dead.  You'd need to have a swarm of 7 or 8 to kill one that fast and if you have 7 or 8 live spiders, you aren't keeping them dead.  That's 7 or 8 potentially leathal explosions that will wander down the hall and kill your raid if you don't keep them busy.  Your job in this case is just to keep the spiders busy.  Killing them is completely unnecessary as long as you keep them from wandering off.</span></td>
