We don't even try to kite/mez them.  A little bad luck and your raid is in trouble.  We just put 4-6 people in each corner and fight them down to start the raid, while MB is targetable, and after MB is down until the RL calls a halt to spider killing.  Bard charm helps a lot.</span></td>
