			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>It's possible to kite them and I have done that before.  But you know how tenuous prox agro in a kite can be and the fact is, I have seen kiters lose one or two spiders which promptly run to the fight room and blow up, wiping the raid.  Enchanter aoe mezzes tend to be a more reliable way, if you can get the people.  One spider leaking through can have tide-turning impact on an MB raid.</span></td>
