				<td colspan="2"><span>The spiders summon.  Swarming / AEing / whatever is a BAD idea.
<br />

<br />
Yes, they can be charmed.  Not a particularly good idea, though.  See summoning thing.
<br />

<br />
Spiders are very easy to kite if you have a corner.  A long time ago (I think I was 62 at the time?  No fade, is all I remember) I was in a pick up raid.  I was assigned a corner with a group. The entire raid had wiped (including my group, cuz it was full of tards that ignored the healer) and I was the last man standing - by a good ten minutes.  Just running around in circles.  Eventually, though, I wanted to start killing them and discovered they summon <img src="/skins/default/images/emotions/emotion-8.gif" border="0" alt="Expressionless" hspace="2" />.
<br />

<br />
